{"tid":25933,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[開定先]外國讀書巴絲點樣搵intern","createTime":"2016-12-06T12:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T14:09:45.000Z","uid":43222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a37f83d8be7e7744f5897e6ea08545980b827b7","tid":25933,"uid":43222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:01:31.000Z","msg":"之前高登開過<br />\n<br />\n我唔係外國讀書，香港三大濕鳩社科yr 3，GDP 3.3，黎緊sem2去英國某 russell group 中下遊嘅U exchange，有D ECA，早兩年一直有係某大報社返過part time <br />\n<br />\n我都知唔係香港好難搵工，特別係intern，所以而家一直都好努力咁搵，sd左十幾封信，已經比人reject左四五間，之前都預左好難搵，但估唔到第一round都過唔到，app test都無得做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔想yr 3都無intern做，仲有讀埋濕鳩科，好驚grad左搵唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇海外巴絲可以分享下外國搵intern經驗，係咪大部分公司都唔會skype in <br />\n<br />\n利申 : 屋企N代貧農無父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d02d06755f1deab98a9edd15dc88b9f83a3c4a81","tid":25933,"uid":11581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:16:47.000Z","msg":"搵唔到 完<br />\n<br />\n利申 講緊我自己"},{"pid":"0bf3a50b83628f51cd79a3bbe354f6b80016d6c2","tid":25933,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:18:59.000Z","msg":"summer intern仲難入過full time"},{"pid":"bf2122a8aaf68aa138560ee9f50b57bb2e671264","tid":25933,"uid":43222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b703bc973b95d519a43fab9b741d0df86a696f17","tid":25933,"uid":56729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T12:24:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主你app test都無得